# Steward (the brain). Copy to .env and fill. Never commit .env.
#
# Most setups need NOTHING here:
#   - Cowork / claude.ai or Claude Desktop on a VPS: model runs on your subscription (no key).
#   - Notion is accessed via the connector (OAuth), not a token.
#
# OPTIONAL — only for a programmatic Raspberry Pi / Agent SDK runtime (no subscription session):
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=
#
# Secrets that belong ELSEWHERE (not in this repo):
#   - Telegram bot token + chat id .......... Concierge Gateway repo's own .env
#   - Notion REST token + database IDs ....... Concierge Gateway repo's own .env
#   - Notion token for the iOS shortcut ...... stored inside the Shortcut on the phone
